</p>
<p>You know what to do from here: in <code>app/Resources/views/genus</code>, create the new
<code>list.html.twig</code> template. Don't forget to extend <code>base.html.twig</code> and then override
the <code>body</code> block. I'll paste a table below to get us started:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="e8fcb4b825">
    <div class="meta">
        <div class="actions">
            <span class="fa fa-clipboard js-activate-clipboard" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Copy Code" data-placement="top"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="info">
                        <span class="js-expand-all" data-range="1-18" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Show All Lines" data-placement="top">
