<h2 id="the-magic-twig-notation">The Magic Twig "." Notation <a class="headerlink" href="twig-dot-syntax#the-magic-twig-notation" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Refresh! Easy - it looks <em>exactly</em> how we want it. But wait a second... something
cool just happened in the background. We printed <code>genus.name</code>... but <code>name</code> is a
<em>private</em> property - so we should <em>not</em> be able to access it directly. How is this
working?</p>
